      <pubDate>Sat, 23 Oct 2021 18:57:19 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>/project/crystal-model/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;This project aims to design 3D models of crystal models and mineral structures that can be visualised on the computer or printed with a 3D printer. All these models can be consulted in the following links:
