    <item>
      <title>Non-existent minerals</title>
      <link>/project/non-existent-minerals/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 23 Oct 2021 19:11:19 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>/project/non-existent-minerals/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;This project, in collaboration with Carlos M. Pina, focuses on disseminating different scientific concepts, with special emphasis on mineralogy, based on the minerals that appear in science fiction and fantasy films, books, comics and video games.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Thanks to this project, we have published two books, held several exhibitions and given numerous talks. For a comprehensive list of these activities see &lt;a href=&#34;../post/dissemination&#34;&gt;dissemination&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>Minerals for foliar fertilization</title>
      <link>/project/foliar-mineral/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Oct 2021 19:11:19 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>/project/foliar-mineral/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;In this project led by Dr. Victoria Fernández, we investigated the usefulness of various minerals in aqueous suspensions for use as foliar fertilisers. To this end, we studied the dissolution kinetics of the minerals and their behaviour in equilibrium. We are also studying other compounds for the development of foliar formulations.
&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
